                <summary>An argument between two brothers on 7/26/1858 ended in murder. Davidson and
                    Michael Gearheart lived near Middlebrook. A disagreement over business led
                    Michael to challenge Davidson to a fight. When Michael picked up a stone,
                    Davidson beat him over the head with a rifle. Michael died two days later.
                    Davidson was arrested and transported to Staunton.</summary>
            </div>
